contentrichtext.text: '''Frederick''', '''Freddie''', or '''Fred Mitchell''' may refer to: * [[Fred Mitchell (baseball)]] (1878–1970), baseball manager of the 1910s * [[F.G. Mitchell]] ({{circa|1885}}–1962), Chairman of Mitchell Construction * [[Frederick John Mitchell]] (1893–1979), Canadian politician * [[Frederick Mitchell (bishop)]] (1901–1979), Anglican bishop in the Church of Ireland * [[Fred Mitchell (artist)]] (born 1923), American abstract expressionist, New York School artist * [[Fred Mitchell (Bahamas)]] (born 1953), foreign minister of the Bahamas * [[Freddie Mitchell]] (born 1978), American football player * [[Freddie Mitchell (EastEnders)]] (appeared 2004–2006) * [[William Frederick Mitchell]] (1845–1914), British naval painter {{hndis|Mitchell, Fred}}
